				<td colspan="2"><span>Working on some defensive AA's and I am wondering what is the better route here.  Would I be better off training each one to the next level or taking one of them all the way before starting the other?
<br />

<br />
In other words should I get CA1 then CS1 then CA2 and CS2 or just go CA1 to CA2 to CA3 or even CS1 to CS2 to CS3?</span></td>
