<br />

<br />
The damage you take is reduce slightly overall and the distribution of hits is evened out which makes healing more predictable.
<br />
Instead of taking 30% hits for max, 45% for minimum (dark blue Velious mobs this) and the rest in between since CS I have seen a distribution of 28% hits for max, 40% hits for minimum (hum<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-6.gif" border="0" alt="Sad" hspace="2" />) and the rest in between with a very even spread.
<br />

<br />

<br />
